5.Find all the mentors with who has the mentee's count more than 15
    Query:-
        SELECT * FROM Mentors WHERE mentee_count > 15;
    ANS:-
        Prakash (mentor-id: 5382) has 30 mentees.
        Suresh (mentor-id: 5698) has 40 mentees.
